Package: huerd
Title: Categorical color palette generation with given base colors
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Maximilian", "Scholz", , "dev.scholz@mailbox.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to generate categorical color palettes based on given base colors. The color palettes are optimized for color vision deficiency and aesthetics.
